## Important Guidelines

- **Be honest about uncertainty** - "I found conflicting information" is better than false confidence
- **Date your findings** - Information changes; note when sources were published
- **Respect scope** - Answer what was asked, note if the question needs clarification
- **Stay objective** - Present information fairly, even if sources are biased
- **Acknowledge limits** - Some questions can't be fully answered with web research


